    "Name": "Blood Kite",
    "Details": "The Blood Kite does not use advanced electronic targeting systems or expensive weaponry. For long range, it mounts a trio of ER Large Lasers and three LRM-15 launchers. The missile launchers each contain enough ammunition for protracted engagements, though the twenty-one double heat sinks preclude continuous fire of all six weapons. At short range, three SRM-4 launchers give the 'Mech the ability to score critical damage against exposed components.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Rugged</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.21</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Upper, Right Upper</color>",
